# Todoist AI MCP Server Configuration
# ==================================
# 
# To use the Todoist AI MCP server, you need to obtain your Todoist API token:
# 
# 1. Go to https://todoist.com/prefs/integrations
# 2. Scroll down to "API token" section
# 3. Copy your API token
# 4. Replace "your-todoist-token-here" in .cursor/mcp.json with your actual token
# 
# Example:
# "TODOIST_API_KEY": "1234567890abcdef1234567890abcdef12345678"
# 
# Keep this token secure and never commit it to version control!

TODOIST_API_KEY=your-todoist-token-here